<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>500 | Server Error</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f14, #1c1c24);
            color: #fff;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .error-box {
            max-width: 520px;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            background: #24242c;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #f3387f;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .error-text {
            color: #b8b8c5;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background: #f3387f;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background: #ff4f8f;
            color: #072654;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-box">
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <div class="error-title">Internal Server Error</div>

        <p class="error-text">
            Something went wrong on our end.<br />
            Please try again later or go back to safety.
        </p>

        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Go to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
